longBusinessSummary: Kshitij Polyline Limited manufactures, distributes, supplies, distributes, and exports lamination equipment and stationery products in India and worl-wide. The company offers industrial products, including nylon coated wires and wiro; PET sheets; PP sheets and Films; and spiral rings. It also offers health care products, such as N 95 masks, PPE kits, industrial mask, face shield, shield, 3 ply masks, fancy masks, and polycarbonate face shield. In addition, it offers stationary products, comprising PP files and folders; lamination materials; binding materials; and ID card accessories. Further, the company provides customized products, including hospital files, printed lanyard, ID cards, and badges, as well as other products including BOPET films, PVC sheets, thermal binding machines, and thermal laminating films. Additionally, it offers equipment, such as ID card making machines; card tipping machine; ID card cutter and printer; and creasing and perforation machine; as well as post printing equipment, comprising spiral binding, comb binding wiro binding, perfect binding, lamination; cold lamination; roll laminator; and slot punch and corner cutter equipment. Kshitij Polyline Limited was founded in 1998 and is headquartered in Mumbai, India.
